Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:08.93,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}愚かでいいのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:08.93,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}我可以懵懂无知吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:13.34,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}見渡す夢の痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:13.34,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}眺望着梦想的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:23.39,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,3000)\be1}さよなら　蒼き日々よ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:23.39,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,3000)\be1}再见了 湛蓝的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:41.80,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}流れに身を任せ　いつか大人になってゆき
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:41.80,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}随波逐流 我们终将长大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:47.90,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}少しずつ汚れてゆく事なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:47.90,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}也代表我们将会逐渐污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:54.01,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}熟した果実だけ　選ばれて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:54.01,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}只选出已经成熟的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:01:01.42,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1800)\be1}ナイフで裂かれて　呑み込まれる前に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:01:01.42,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1800)\be1}在以刀刃切开吞噬之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:06.03,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}僕等は目指した　Shangri-La
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:06.03,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}我们所向往的香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:09.22,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}欲望は抑えきれずに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:09.22,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}无法压抑己身的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:15.30,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}空想にまみれた　「自由」を求め続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:15.30,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}沉浸于幻想 不断追求自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:21.77,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}今なら言えるだろう　此処がそう楽園さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:21.77,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}现在就敢如此断言吧 这里就是所谓的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:28.75,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,2000)\be1}さよなら　蒼き日々よ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:28.75,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,2000)\be1}再见了 湛蓝的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:31.56,ED_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}眩しすぎる朝は　「諦め」誘うんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:31.56,ED_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}过于耀眼的早晨 不禁使人心灰意冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.63,0:22:42.41,ED_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}全てさらけ出して　この身を委ねる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.63,0:22:42.41,ED_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}表明一切 献出己身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:48.50,ED_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}握りしめた冷たい指　君は悲しく笑い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:48.50,ED_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}握着冰冷的手指 你悲伤地露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.62,0:22:54.52,ED_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}僕はかける言葉もなく　景色は滲む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.62,0:22:54.52,ED_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我无言以对 景色逐渐模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.62,0:23:00.36,ED_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}始まればいずれ終わる　綺麗事などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.62,0:23:00.36,ED_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}有开始终将会结束 一切都无须粉饰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:03.40,ED_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}せめて君を温めたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:03.40,ED_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}希望至少能温暖你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:13.03,ED_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}ほんの少しの時間を与えて　神様
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:13.03,ED_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}神啊 再给我一点时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多数异界体正从西南方接近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计再三十分钟抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是群体行动的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒带头的就赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集群防御系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一、第二灵智型部队在西南方岛屿迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三、第四、第五部队在本岛西南沿岸布下防线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:02:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那些来自宇宙的鼠辈见识一下人类的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以见识到人类军的本事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他们连所罗门系统都还不会使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旺兹是位优秀的指挥官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会这么轻易败北
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会祈祷他们不要重蹈摩达维亚的覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在CDC是人类军的指挥总部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去那里又能做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连系统都不会用的人 我怎么能信赖他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想以这种方式跟你重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛耶 你要做什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先待在里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能够活在世界上的某处 就是我唯一上战场的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我走太慢才害你跟不上大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦 不过你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我才刚到外面来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不太适应怎么走路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就边休息边走吧 不要太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意听我一个请求吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 要我背你都没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你可以当我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连一个朋友都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友不就在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 小芹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有自我介绍过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是避难所的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芹就跟大家在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫做乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城不就是总士学长的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说定罗 我们要当朋友喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 - 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一波动屏障被消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人没有变更前进路线 正笔直往这里前进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直线前进吗 竟敢瞧不起我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 已经取得外出许可了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思 我是为了比较虚弱的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时候人类彼此却…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤 你在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事情要麻烦当初把我放到系统里面的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生至今第一次来到外界 所以我还不太会走路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你拿一个可以载我移动的东西过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二波动屏障被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校也卯足全力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说对吧 卡农
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也比平常还有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚去见我以前的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神剑型法夫那要出马罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在西南方登陆 自爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是昂宿型的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Triple SIX 前往支援！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就到罗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡农 带第三部队绕到左边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要夹击它们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险 在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 连无线通讯都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 Mark III！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体表面跟皮肤的触感同步的程度居然这么高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体好沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是神剑型的特征
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快和它同化并接受变性意识
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐 站起来打 不然会没命的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城…乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次这样跟你说话呢 千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:07:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨蛇级潜水舰被击中 三艘都被击沈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的首领呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知另外的两艘潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对西南部沿岸进行密集攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己人也一起打？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有生以来第一次玩泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 只是表面烧掉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要选择是从现在才开始喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西方出现了第三群
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这座岛的西南部份切离 用系统让它自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把登陆的敌人和岛屿一起炸掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎击系统自行运作 拒绝我们的手动控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会动？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在操纵的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法查明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃饭了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是什么状况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总部、总部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 接不通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指挥系统似乎被截断了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情势正有所变化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉让我们离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？这是谁干的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是那一边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来好像是想要引导我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新建立防线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能动的家伙通通到前面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量的昂宿型异界体在龙宫山顶集结
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我们正上方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是岛的痛楚传到我身上而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一你有什么三长两短…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我躲起来的话 这座岛一定会沉没的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前 我必须让大家做出选择
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙骨区块 (Keel Block)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兀尔德之泉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是强迫要接受的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以自己的意志重新选择吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别发呆了 快上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要驾驶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.73,0:11:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不穿作用服？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑也曾经没换装就驾驶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在不战斗就对不起我爸跟甲洋他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作是给予大家想要得到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让大家再做一次选择 确定所要的究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这对异界体也是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要请它们做选择
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我才会诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤回去吧 避难所还很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你陪我来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为系统的研究员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 身为岛上的居民我要亲眼见证一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被引导来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门的本体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟王之室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第二CDC吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本构造跟CDC一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认所有系统
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把龙宫岛的主控权拿回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是这座岛 这座岛就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在岛上的人们想将岛变成什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些人们的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们实际上在追求什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让人们得以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的只有请他们做出选择
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.23,0:13:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让人们得以理解…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初我没能让你做出选择…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也选择过罗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有自我 这就是我的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在这里喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前有117只登陆 敌方势力更加扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昂宿型会发现这里只是时间上的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二防卫系统呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在执行中 再两分钟完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,群体中诞生的主体将索敌系统无效化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法发现本体！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以拿法夫那当诱饵 引诱出敌人的首领吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很难 但我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌声？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门有反应了 是敌人首领
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将所有迎击系统集中起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌声的来源在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是龙宫岛西边的灯塔 我把影像显示在荧幕上面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要让异界体选择吗 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人本体开始朝灯塔移动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有法夫那散开 立刻往岛的西边移动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避开敌人前往指示的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要攻击敌人的本体！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么敌人我都会打倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕、好可怕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲吧 高拜！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的动作…是驾驶员换人了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡农 找到敌方首领了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们往西边移动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他还可以动的也跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底飞弹准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark V以神盾系统阻止敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark VIII绕到右侧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark III确认敌方核心并且将其破坏！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊 剑司！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准去 维持阵型！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.15,0:16:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连神剑型也抵挡不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标再度朝灯塔移动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城乙姬呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有移动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你们也选好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有对话的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会消失的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚无的道路…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做选择的并不是只有你们喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬 我们逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么机体？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挡下来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 会被炸掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的核心正从内部被消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道异界体…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒被同化了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标又开始消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门的反应消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要寻找就找得到喔 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振动、各种波形、温度、电子、电波、空间相位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架机体攻击之后所留下来的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员 你听得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的位置捕捉到了 帮忙打倒那家伙吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…骑…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要跟系统同步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能跟Mark XI那时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你还在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士 你曾经说过只有这座岛是唯一的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初我不懂这句话的含意 也不知道你在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是听你的话去战斗而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在我觉得有点懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你一直很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我们一无所知的时候 你就想要保护这座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是翔子还有甲洋那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也独自背负着痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架机体的识别代号是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark Zein
